nodes.text: Good evening,     It two weeks since I finished chemo &  I not sure when this happen , but I have noticed my right big toe has a small amount of puss coming out of it. I did cut my toe nails down a week ago but didn notice any cut. I going to clean it with peroxide and see what happens. I also have an appt with Dr.Person1 on MM/DD/YYYY I can show him at that time also.
